{"tid":2412562,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《時尚惡女：庫伊拉》預告曝光！Emma Stone魔性笑聲讓人爆雞皮...見證迪士尼最狂反派誕生","createTime":"2021-02-18T06:01:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T17:31:06.000Z","uid":41343,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"910a0214ae01b59adf00bcff2e6e93aebaa09471","tid":2412562,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T06:01:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/U_WhJAEMWY4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FU_WhJAEMWY4&d=3nH4Hj8OzEJ%2Fsn4LiTBSOirXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=1f922c7a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/U_WhJAEMWY4</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這根本就是小丑＋哈莉奎茵的綜合版啊！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由奧斯卡影后艾瑪史東（Emma Stone）主演、預計將在今年5月28日於美國上映的 101 忠狗前傳電影《時尚惡女：庫伊拉》（Cruella）絕對不容錯過！<br />\n<br />\n迪士尼全新真人版電影《時尚惡女：庫伊拉》昨晚首度公佈了前導海報與首支預告，過去多以甜美形象示人的艾瑪史東，這次挑戰迪士尼經典反派角色「庫伊拉」整個人改頭換面！海報中的黑白爆炸頭造型，帶著濃厚的龐克搖滾風格，十足展現出更潮、更酷的時尚態度，讓人幾乎快認不出來她就是美國甜心艾瑪史東，影迷期待度爆表！"},{"pid":"48db806d53213fadc8b15fe8007e07f58cb31b33","tid":2412562,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T06:05:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaed29054677a6f9028d71dcccde4a7caceb7aab","tid":2412562,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T07:05:46.000Z","msg":"斑點狗前傳？"},{"pid":"98fa7a77089e202eb62f575f960913a5c8096c05","tid":2412562,"uid":63909,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T07:07:20.000Z","msg":"無黑人無LGBT<br />\n點睇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fa750b2d7e1759508d76ebd28c818a3d5eaa1a2","tid":2412562,"uid":306337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98fa7a77089e202eb62f575f960913a5c8096c05","tid":2412562,"uid":63909,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T07:07:20.000Z","msg":"無黑人無LGBT<br />\n點睇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-1